e-mechanism-layer-maps [anatomy meta-001], allow-analytic-extremizer-over-computation [vasseur-pressure S2-E008], adversarial-review-needs-complete-parallel-context [S2-E007], adversarial-synthesis-goal-structure update [S2-E007], require-sensitivity-table-for-proof-analysis [S2-E001], one-task-per-exploration [E007], ask-what-replaces-the-bottleneck [E008], flag-cross-framework-connections [E006].)

